228
00:19:51,880 --> 00:19:55,350
I gotta tell ya... I'm a little scared, Hi.

229
00:19:55,440 --> 00:19:58,000
- How come is that, honey?
- Well...

230
00:19:58,080 --> 00:20:01,470
We got a baby, Hi.
It's an awful big responsibility.

231
00:20:01,560 --> 00:20:04,518
Honey, could you slide over a tad
and raise the nipper up?

232
00:20:04,600 --> 00:20:08,832
