235
00:20:18,640 --> 00:20:21,712
- Now, you're gonna help, aren't you?
- How's that, honey?

236
00:20:21,800 --> 00:20:25,270
Contribute to the management of the child.

237
00:20:26,560 --> 00:20:29,028
- Quiet evenings together.
- You can count on it.

238
00:20:29,120 --> 00:20:31,998
Everything decent and normal
