280
00:24:56,640 --> 00:24:58,915
I mean, we got a toddler here.

281
00:25:01,680 --> 00:25:04,114
Say, who wears the pants round here, H I?

282
00:25:05,840 --> 00:25:09,116
- Honey, these boys just got outta the joint...
