292
00:26:11,840 --> 00:26:14,229
Tonight and tomorrow, tops.

293
00:26:17,320 --> 00:26:19,629
<i>That night I had a dream.</i>

294
00:26:20,320 --> 00:26:24,950
<i>I drifted off, thinkin'about
