306
00:27:19,480 --> 00:27:23,553
<i>But I feared that I myself had unleashed him.</i>

307
00:27:26,920 --> 00:27:29,878
<i>For he was the fury that would be,</i>

308
00:27:29,960 --> 00:27:33,953
<i>as soon as Florence Arizona
