425
00:36:54,680 --> 00:36:56,875
Ed has a friend at one of the agencies.

426
00:36:56,960 --> 00:37:00,669
Maybe she can help me and Dot.
There's somethin' wrong with my semen.

427
00:37:00,760 --> 00:37:03,035
