428
00:37:03,120 --> 00:37:05,236
Ed. Ed Junior.

429
00:37:05,320 --> 00:37:09,677
- But I thought you said it was a boy.
- Well, as in Edward. We just like that name.

430
00:37:09,760 --> 00:37:12,513
It's a good one.
I don't really need another kid,

431
00:37:12,600 --> 00:37:15,239
but Dot says these are
gettin' too big to cuddle.

432
00:37:15,320 --> 00:37:17,311
Say, that reminds me...

433
00:37:18,320 --> 00:37:21,312
Mind you don't cut yourself, Mordecai.

